description:
The Hulk is alone at last! But the Red She-Hulk learns the shocking fate of Bruce Banner – and explodes with rage! By Jason Aaron and Jefte Palo!

The Red Hulk and Machine Man battle the awesome Sultan Magus in the heart of his power! By Jeff Parker and Patch Zircher!

Collects:

  • Incredible Hulk #7.1
  • Hulk #45-47
